---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="關於作者 | 下班後理財"
    description="了解「下班後理財」的開發初衷與獨立開發者的理財哲學。"
>
    <main class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden pb-24">
        <!-- Background Decorations -->
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-7xl h-[600px] -z-10 pointer-events-none"
        >
            <div
                class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-blue-100 rounded-full blur-[100px] opacity-40 animate-pulse"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="absolute top-40 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-40 animate-pulse"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <div
            class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-16 md:pt-24 max-w-5xl relative z-10"
        >
            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <div class="text-center mb-20 space-y-6 animate-fade-in-down">
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border border-blue-100"
                >
                    Independent Developer Project
                </div>
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight leading-tight"
                >
                    這裡沒有公司，<br /><span class="text-blue-600"
                        >只有追求極致的開發者</span
                    >
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
                >
                    我是一位獨立工程師。為了做出自己心中理想的理財工具，我決定動手實現它，並將它分享給與我有一樣需求的你。
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-start">
                <!-- Left: Story -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-12">
                    <section
                        class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 relative group overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 text-slate-100 text-8xl font-serif select-none pointer-events-none group-hover:text-blue-50 transition-colors"
                        >
                            “
                        </div>
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm"
                                >01</span
                            >
                            為什麼要做這件事？
                        </h2>
                        <div
                            class="prose prose-lg prose-slate text-slate-600 space-y-6 leading-relaxed"
                        >
                            <p>
                                身為一名工程師，我對「效率」與「數位隱私」有著近乎偏執的追求。長期以來，我一直在尋找一個能夠一眼看清資產現況，同時又不需要把家產帳目上傳到雲端的工具。
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                我發現許多理財 App
                                不是充滿了推銷廣告，就是介面過於繁瑣。於是，我利用下班時間，從第一行程式碼開始，打造了「下班後理財」。
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                這不是一個大型公司的產品。這是一個工程師為了優化生活、解決問題所交出的答卷。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section
                        class="bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl text-white relative overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500 rounded-full blur-[100px] opacity-20"
                        >
                        </div>
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-white"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="w-8 h-8 bg-white rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-slate-900 text-sm"
                                >02</span
                            >
                            我的開發哲學
                        </h2>
                        <div
                            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative z-10 font-sans"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="space-y-3 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
                            >
                                <span class="text-blue-400 text-2xl">🔒</span>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">隱私即服務</h4>
                                <p
                                    class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed"
                                >
                                    工具不應該以數據換取免費。本站所有資料皆儲存在您的本地瀏覽器，這是最安全的防線。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="space-y-3 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
                            >
                                <span class="text-purple-400 text-2xl">⚡</span>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">直覺大於繁瑣</h4>
                                <p
                                    class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed"
                                >
                                    捨棄細碎的記帳流程。我更在乎資產大方向的成長與分散風險，讓工具服務人，而非人服務工具。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="space-y-3 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
                            >
                                <span class="text-emerald-400 text-2xl">📈</span
                                >
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">數據驅動決策</h4>
                                <p
                                    class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed"
                                >
                                    將冰冷的數字視覺化。無論是稅務壓力還是 Coast
                                    FIRE
                                    進度，視覺化的資料能幫助您做出更理性的選擇。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div
                                class="space-y-3 p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10"
                            >
                                <span class="text-amber-400 text-2xl">☕</span>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">純粹的體驗</h4>
                                <p
                                    class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed"
                                >
                                    沒有註冊、沒有通知、沒有廣告。這裡只有最單純、功能完整的理財計算機。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>

                <!-- Right: Side Card -->
                <div class="space-y-8 lg:sticky lg:top-8">
                    <!-- Creator Card -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm text-center"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl shadow-inner border border-blue-50"
                        >
                            👨‍💻
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                            關於作者：路易斯
                        </h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            一位熱愛技術與投資的獨立開發者。我致力於透過技術解決生活中的痛點，並相信工具的本質應該是簡單且充滿力量。
                        </p>
                        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-50 space-y-3">
                            <p
                                class="text-xs text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold"
                            >
                                目前進度
                            </p>
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <div class="flex justify-between text-xs mb-1">
                                    <span class="text-slate-600 font-medium"
                                        >功能開發 (V1.2)</span
                                    >
                                    <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold"
                                        >進行中</span
                                    >
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="w-full bg-slate-100 h-1.5 rounded-full overflow-hidden"
                                >
                                    <div
                                        class="bg-blue-600 h-full w-[85%] rounded-full"
                                    >
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- CTA / Spread the word -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-indigo-700 rounded-3xl p-8 text-white shadow-xl shadow-blue-200"
                    >
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">覺得有幫助嗎？</h4>
                        <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            這是一個完全免費的專案。如果您覺得這個工具縮短了您理財的時間，歡迎將它分享給身邊的朋友。您的支持是我持續更新最大的動力！
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="mailto:a401120174@gmail.com"
                            class="block w-full text-center bg-white text-blue-600 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors shadow-sm"
                        >
                            聯絡作者
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
    .animate-fade-in-down {
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    }
</style>
